scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Pieces included: 1 score, 1 CD, 1 submission letter. Notes: There is a third piece titled A nonfunctional teapot, by this composer listed in the submission letter but the piece is not in the collection. Note on envelope: RT1.1 .07, RT1.2 .06, RT1.3 .07..
